                                Kashkar</persName>, with whom he has sometimes been confused (by
                            Wright, among others).</desc>
                    </relation>
                    <relation type="disambiguation" ref="http://syriaca.org/keyword/distinct-entity" mutual="http://syriaca.org/person/1086 http://syriaca.org/person/320" source="#bib1086-2">
                        <desc xml:lang="en">
                            <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/1086">Aba of Kashkar</persName>
                            should be distinguished from <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/320">Abraham of Kashkar</persName>,
                            despite a note by Assemani that could seem to imply their
                            identity.</desc>
